      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">About the Election</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        There are <strong>two City Council seats</strong> up for election in 2025, each for a 4-year term. Aberdeen residents who meet eligibility requirements may vote in the municipal election.
      </p>
