      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Running for Office</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Residents wishing to run for election can pick up a <strong>Candidate Packet</strong> at the Finance window on the first floor of City Hall during normal business hours (Mon–Fri, 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM). Contact the City Clerk for more information.
      </p>
